{"tid":252835,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰香港裁員約600人 中高層四人炒一人","createTime":"2017-05-22T01:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T06:18:23.000Z","uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a15e646718ed8dfa46a4d5e5200b6ebfb3543234","tid":252835,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170522/large/1495414729_94c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170522%2Flarge%2F1495414729_94c8.jpg&h=6e76c49a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前預告會裁員的國泰航空（293）今日宣佈，將裁員約600名香港總部員工，作為企業精簡轉型一部份。<br />\n<br />\n是次裁員影響國泰香港總部員工，包括中高級管理層及非管理人員職位，當中國泰裁190個高級和中級管理員工，佔25%管理職位，另外裁員400個非管理人員職位，佔集團相關職位約18%。<br />\n<br />\n大部份被裁員工將今日及未來一個月收到調動或停職通知。大部份重組變動於2017年底完成。被裁減而要離職的員工可得到最多額外!2個月的薪金、延長員工醫療福利等等d 1<br />\n<br />\n國泰表示，裁員不影響前線地勤員工、機師及機艙服務員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56725198&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56725198%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170522&d=q6lxkNJLkMCZuErjOs479LZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=fe49dd0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56725198%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170522&h=282f8712\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56725198&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170522</a><br />\n<br />\n//IT部有冇份? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cab288914a54846ad8b8857ba8bb289abced9a","tid":252835,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T01:31:32.000Z","msg":"飛雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec52c6a3e5afae4